rows.label: tlk43300011_01_msg0001
rows.name:
In the heat of battle, everything's
about location, location, location.

rows.label: tlk43300011_01_msg0002
rows.name:
If you move round to your opponent's
blind spot, it'll be much easier for
your attacks to connect.

rows.label: tlk43300011_01_msg0003
rows.name:
My old man practically drilled that
into me. Used to be a merc, don'cha
know.

rows.label: tlk43300011_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I really take after the guy,
don't you think? ...Well, actually
I guess you wouldn't know!
